          "talkerSpriteName": "supporter-default",
          "speechTexts": [
            "Welcome <b>Master</b> to join <b>Campaign RC-001</b>. I am a <b>Supporter</b>, the <b>Smart Bots</b> assigned to help you get used to this job.",
            "Okay, now let's go to the mission destination, <b>Planet A-867</b>. There are currently our people there. They encountered some small trouble at <b>The Mine</b> so they called us for help."
          ]
        },
        {
          "talker": 1,
          "talkerSpriteName": "supporter-excited",
          "speechTexts": [
            "Let me tell you a little bit, what they exploit is <b>\"The Energy Mine\"</b> used as fuel for me. I heard rumors that it's delicious, oh, how much to look forward to this trip! Don't you think so, <b>Master</b>?"
